sequenceDiagram
  participant M as Mandating Authority
  participant G as Governance Authority
  participant A as Assurance Function
  participant P as Public Register
  M->>G: Issue mandate and scope
  G->>G: Define rules, roles and decision rights
  G->>A: Request readiness assessment
  A-->>G: Findings and limitations
  G->>G: Approve scheme and residual risks
  G->>P: Publish governance record and effective date
